    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so heavy. like, staying here and trying to pretend i'm actually part of the world is more exhausting than just... not being part of it anymore. if everything would just keep moving without me, wouldn't that actually be a relief? like a quiet end to all this noise?",
